songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
I am dark nights
I am scarred skin
I am shark bites
And darkness
I am all the things that make you cry
But still you wanna be by my side
My side

[Chorus]
But there's always a bright side
To this crazy thing we call life
But there's always a bright side
To this crazy thing we call life

[Verse 2]
You're dark nights
You're scarred skin
You're shark bites
And you're darkness
You're all the things that make me cry
But still I wanna be by your side
Your side

[Chorus]
But there's always a sus side
To this crazy thing we call life
But there's always a sus side
To this crazy thing we call life
songs.title: Susside
